# About Us

We are the <span class="h3">Cornell Undergraduate Research Board</span>, and our mission is to connect you with exciting research opportunities and people.

<div class="row post text-center" style="text-align: justify">
<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="{{site.url}}/images/diagrams/billboard.png" class="icon">
<p>Forums, from the <a href="{{site.url}}/pages/events/forums.html">Fall and Spring research forums</a> to the <a href="{{site.url}}/pages/events/humanities.html">Humanities Showcase</a>, combine campus-wide poster sessions and research keynotes.</p>
</div>

<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="{{site.url}}/images/diagrams/pmp.png">
<p>Our <a href="pmp-about.html"><span class="bigger">Peer Mentorship Program</span></a> helps you map out your research path with a mentor.</p>
</div>

<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="{{site.url}}/images/diagrams/dinners.png">
<p>Our <a href="dinner-series.html"><span class="bigger">Dinner Series</span></a> bring together students and faculty to share a meal and talk science.</p>
</div>
</div>

{{{section_end}}}

